1 WHEREAS, it is fitting to offer an expression of friendship, respect, admiration, and
2 spiritual solidarity between the people of Louisiana and the Holy See.
3 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
4 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend His Holiness Pope Leo XIV for his faithful
5 leadership of the Catholic Church; does hereby extend wishes for strength, wisdom, health,
6 and divine guidance for his pontificate and pastoral mission; and does hereby affirm an
7 enduring commitment to faith, compassion, human dignity, peace among nations, and
8 service to one another.
